</div></div><!-- end item --><div class="item clearfix"><h4><a href="https://popular-archaeology.com/author/mtitienohoumamsaad/">Marek Titien Olszewski and Houmam Saad</a></h4><div class="author-list-bio"><p class="p4"><span class="s1" style="color: #000000"><strong>Marek Titien Olszewski</strong>&nbsp;is Associate Professor, PhD from the Sorbonne, lecturer at the Institute of Archaeology, University of Warsaw, specialist in Roman archaeology and iconography, and an expert on ancient mosaics, Roman archaeology and Syria (UNESCO). He sits on the board of the AIEMA (Association Internationale pour l&rsquo;Etude de la Mosa&iuml;que Antiqua).</span></p>
